data.title: Sony Xperia P Technical Specifications
data.meta_description: Check Specifications of the Sony Xperia P. Find out all about the device specifications!
data.text:
IMEI Unlock Check

Learn the unlock/lock status of the iPhone by its IMEI number.

IMEI Blacklist Check

Enter the IMEI code to know whether the iPhone is blacklisted or not by carriers.

IMEI iCloud Check

Find out your iPhone iCloud status by entering the device's IMEI number.

IMEI Stolen Check

Use IMEI to see the lost and stolen statuses of Apple iPhones. All models are supported.

IMEI SIM Lock Check

Check any iPhone's IMEI code to learn its carrier SIM lock details.

IMEI Carrier Check

Learn carrier information by using the iPhone IMEI code and our check service.

IMEI MDM Check

See iPhone MDM/DEP lock status by entering its IMEI number.

IMEI Warranty Check

Learn the iPhone warranty status via its IMEI code.

AT&T IMEI Check

Run AT&T IMEI Checker to learn carrier Lock/Unlock and AT&T blacklist statuses via IMEI number.

Verizon IMEI Check

Use VERIZON IMEI check service to learn carrier Lock/Unlock and blacklist status. Enter IMEI to get details.
